| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-7378 — Recovery Inhibition (killsec)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 9ef3f27c-b19f-5b1d-bdf5-5bb6439ca92c"
